channel.title: I just need help
channel.description: Ever since I started playing Runescape, I always have wanted to own and work on my own RSPS... The only problem is, I dont understand coding at all... and the tutorials confuse me. I need someone to email me back and forth, or maybe even over phone, to talk me through coding and starting a server step by step. Please send me an email. ajskewes@hotmail.com
